            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJob%2020%3A1-22%3A30%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_20_1%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJob%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EZophar%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Second%20Response%20to%20Job%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Zophar%20the%20Naamathite%20replied%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_20_2%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20must%20reply%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebecause%20I%20am%20greatly%20disturbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_20_3%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EI%26%23x2019%3Bve%20had%20to%20endure%20your%20insults%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20now%20my%20spirit%20prompts%20me%20to%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_20_4%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20you%20realize%20that%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20time%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eever%20since%20people%20were%20first%20placed%20on%20the%20earth%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22job_20_5%22%20bk%3D%22job%22%20ch%3D%2220%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20triumph%20of%20the%20wicked%20has%20been%20short%20lived%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp